cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/68282/', '', 'Tetracaine, Azelastine, Ketotifen, Desloratadine', 'Vilazodone, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Bupropion', 1767369485);
